%p Would you be interested in being a beta tester/customer for our Online Pet Care Network starting in October?
%p If so, please provide and email where we can contact you.

= form_for @lead do |f|
  -if @lead.errors.any?
    #error_explanation
      %h2= "#{pluralize(@lead.errors.count, "error")} prohibited your email from being saved:"
      %ul
        - @lead.errors.full_messages.each do |msg|
          %li= msg

  .field
    = f.label :email
    = f.text_field :email
  .actions
    = f.submit 'Save'
